eppe Francica-Nava de Bontif\u00e8]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Santi Giovanni e Paolo, Rome|Cardinal-Priest of Santi Giovanni e Paolo]]|years=19 December 1929&nbsp;\u2013 2 March 1939}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Francis Joseph Spellman]]}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Rafael Merry del Val]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Archpriest of St. Peter's Basilica]]|years=25 March 1930&nbsp;\u2013 2 March 1939}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Federico Tedeschini]]}}\n{{s-bef|rows=1|before=[[Pietro Gasparri]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Cardinal Secretary of State]]|years=9 February 1930&nbsp;\u2013 10 February 1939}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Luigi Maglione]]}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Lorenzo Lauri]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Camerlengo of the Sacred College of Cardinals]]|years=1937&nbsp;\u2013 2 March 1939}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Federico Tedeschini]]}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Pope Pius XI|Pius XI]]|rows=2}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Grand Masters and Lieutenancies of the Order of the Holy Sepulchre|Grand Master]]<br>of the [[Order of the Holy Sepulchre]]|years=2 March 1939&nbsp;\u2013 16 July 1940}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Nicola Cardinal Canali]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Pope]]|years=2 March 1939&nbsp;\u2013 9 October 1958}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Pope John XXIII|John XXIII]]}}\n{{s-end}}\n\n{{Pope Pius XII}}\n{{Popes}}\n{{History of the Catholic Church}}\n\n{{Subject bar\n|portal1        = Biography\n|portal2        = Christianity\n|portal3        = Italy\n|portal4        = Vatican City\n|commons        = y\n|commons-search = Category:Pius XII\n|q              = y\n|q-search       = Pope Pius XII\n|s              = y\n|s-search       = Author:Pius XII\n|d              = y\n|d-search       = Q2604\n}}\n{{Authority control}}\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Pius Xii, Pope}}\n[[Category:Pope Pius XII| ]]<!--please leave the empty space as standard-->\n[[Category:1876 births]]\n[[Category:1958 deaths]]\n[[Category:19th-century Italian people]]\n[[Category:20th-century Italian people]]\n[[Category:Almo Collegio Capranica alumni]]\n[[Category:Apostolic Nuncios to Bavaria|Pacelli]]\n[[Category:Apostolic Nuncios to 