]]\n|M83\n|[[Mah\u00e9-class minesweeper|''Mah\u00e9'' Class]]\n|16 May 1983\n|15 May 2006\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[INS Malpe|INS '' Malpe'']]\n|M86\n|[[Mah\u00e9-class minesweeper|''Mah\u00e9'' Class]]\n|10 May 1984\n|04 Dec 2006\n|\n|\n|-\n! colspan=\"7\" style=\"background: lavender;\" |Inshore Minesweeper\n|-\n|[[INS Bassein|INS ''Bassein'']]\n|M2707\n|[[Ham-class minesweeper|''Ham'' class]]\n|14 June 1955<ref name=Singh_bluewater>Singh, Satyindra, Blueprint to Blue Water - The Indian Navy 1951\u20131965 ; pub Lancer New Delhi 1992, {{ISBN|978-81-7062-148-5}}</ref>\n|1994\n|\n|ex-Royal Navy {{HMS|Littleham|M2707|6}}\n|-\n|[[INS Bimlipatan|INS ''Bimlipatan'']]\n|M2705\n|[[Ham-class minesweeper|''Ham'' class]]\n|14 June 1955<ref name=Singh_bluewater/>\n|1994\n|\n|ex-Royal Navy {{HMS|Hildersham|M2705|6}}\n|-\n|}\n\n===Fast Attack Craft===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n|-\n! style=\"text-align:left; width:15%;background-color:#3399FF;\"|Ship\n! style=\"text-align:left; width:5%;background-color:#3399FF;\"|Pennant\n! style=\"text-align:left; width:15%;background-color:#3399FF;\"|Class\n! style=\"text-align:left; width:10%;background-color:#3399FF;\"|Commissioned\n! style=\"text-align:left; width:10%;background-color:#3399FF;\"|Decommissioned\n! style=\"text-align:left; width:12%;background-color:#3399FF;\"|Fate\n! style=\"text-align:left; width:25%;background-color:#3399FF;\"|Notes\n|-\n! colspan=\"7\" style=\"background: lavender;\" | Missile Boat\n|-\n| {{INS|Veer|K82|6}} || K82 || [[Vidyut-class missile boat|''Vidyut'' Class]] || 2 April 1971 || 31 December 1982<ref name=Hiranandani/> || ||Sunk [[PNS Muhafiz|PNS ''Muhafiz'']] during [[Operation Trident (1971)]].\n|-\n| {{INS|Nirbhik|K88|6}} || K88 || [[Vidyut-class missile boat|''Vidyut'' Class]] || 20 February 1971 || 31 December 1986<ref name=Hiranandani/> || ||\n|-\n| {{INS|Nipat|K86|6}} || K86 || [[Vidyut-class missile boat|''Vidyut'' Class]] || 26 April 1971 || 29 February 1988<ref name=Hiranandani/> || || Destroyed th